snippet.title: Arcade Longplay [990] Rabbit Punch (US)
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: KAGE-008

Overseas localization of the original Japanese game 'Rabio Lepus'. This game requires to be completed twice in order to properly finish it, which is what I did here. You get different endings depending on whether you played the Normal or Expert loop (both obviously included in this video), but those got modified and you no longer get the rabbit girl scenes from the Japanese version.

Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
